        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><b>Water Resources Research Amendments Act</b></p> <p>This bill reauthorizes through FY2025 the Water Resources Research Act Program and otherwise revises the program, including by increasing the federal share of grant funding under the program for water resources research and technology institutes.</p> </p>]]>
        </text>
